  "detailed_description": "Tired of lead, rubber, pointy objects and a constant fear of impending doom?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThen you should try Butterfly Moment, where all you have to do, is catch pretty little butterflies while admiring great views on a lush island.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Catch butterflies from stationary positions with your magic net.<br />\r\n- Unlock new zones by catching more butterflies.<br />\r\n- Travel (Teleport) between zones at any time.<br />\r\n- Enjoy a unique and beautiful view from each zone.<br />\r\n- Set your own pace.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRelax, unwind and let your rhythm guide you.  Visit Butterfly Island.",
  "about_the_game": "Tired of lead, rubber, pointy objects and a constant fear of impending doom?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThen you should try Butterfly Moment, where all you have to do, is catch pretty little butterflies while admiring great views on a lush island.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Catch butterflies from stationary positions with your magic net.<br />\r\n- Unlock new zones by catching more butterflies.<br />\r\n- Travel (Teleport) between zones at any time.<br />\r\n- Enjoy a unique and beautiful view from each zone.<br />\r\n- Set your own pace.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRelax, unwind and let your rhythm guide you.  Visit Butterfly Island.",
